<paragraph blockId="52.[178,1085,254,373]" box="[178,1025,254,281]" pageId="52" pageNumber="57">
Abb. des 3 bei 
<bibRefCitation author="WESTRICH P" box="[323,521,256,276]" pageId="52" pageNumber="57" pagination="3 - 8001" refId="ref38627" refString="WESTRICH P. (1989): Die Wildbienen Baden-Wurttembergs. Bd. 1 und 2. - 972 S. Stuttgart (Ulmer). ISBN 3 - 8001 - 3307 - 5." type="book chapter" year="1989">WESTRICH 1989: 593</bibRefCitation>
, Abb. des 
<specimenCount box="[618,637,260,281]" pageId="52" pageNumber="57" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
bei MÜLLER, KREBS &amp; AMIET 1997: 183.
</paragraph>
